### Test Blob Ingestion - Ingest all supported files from a blob path
POST {{ingestionUrl}}/ingestion/blob
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "blobPath": "docs/",
  "containerName": "documents",
  "tags": ["documentation", "blob-ingestion"],
  "metadata": {
    "source": "blob-storage",
    "ingestedBy": "test-user"
  }
}

### Test Blob Ingestion - Specific file
POST {{ingestionUrl}}/ingestion/blob
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "blobPath": "api-specs/my-api.yaml",
  "tags": ["api", "openapi"]
}

### Test HTML Ingestion
POST {{ingestionUrl}}/ingestion/html
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test HTML Document",
  "sourceUrl": "https://example.com/test.html",
  "tags": ["test", "html"],
  "content": "<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><title>Test</title></head><body><h1>Test Document</h1><p>This is a test HTML document.</p></body></html>"
}
